fields.customfield_10312: AB testing set-up per ticket request
fields.description:
+*Objective*+
 * Optimize viewability of banner on HP without negative impact on engagement.

+*Implementation*+
 * Move banner BTF to ATF (above categories)
 * Original banner size - MREC
 * We only call 320x50 and 300x50 when we move it ATF
 * We use a unique KV for this banner Adpos = MREC_2_HP_M
 * We only expand that space when there is a banner so make sure there is no blank space on the page. 

+*AB testing set-up*+
 * Experimental traffic - all
 * Control - current design (MREC)
 * Testing - moving banner (320x50 & 300x50)
fields.summary: Improve warning when automatic ctor/dtor are enabled

comments.body:
[~jseverins] [~leslava] 

Suggest we use a different KV for this ATF banner to track easily. Let me know if u agree.
[~ropetrescu] need your help on the measurement plan. We intend to keep the volume small to avoid risk.

Let's use Adpos = MREC_2_HP_M

[~leslava] can you please update the sheet?
the Metrics is conversion of srp page.

automation: [http://ci.optimus.dev.ebayc3.com/job/bolt-go-release_master/job/QA-Automation-Pandaren-EarlyBird/616/HTML_Report/]

 

As all the changes is related with Home page, however, none of the failed cases is about za home page mobile. So it is stable .
